Nick Cousins and wife Herminia Garcia charged with wilful neglect after daughter Blanca Cousins fell to her death from luxury apartment in Hong Kong on Tuesday . 
  Mr Cousins was also arrested on suspicion of 'ill treatment' after it emerged her birth had not been registered . 
  He left court clutching his wife and was visibly upset after she was granted bail . 
  Blanca fell from the 19th floor of their luxury apartment . 
  Her birth and that of her sister were never registered . 
  She was found dead at the foot of the building on Tuesday in an apparent suicide . 
  Her father was also charged but has not been charged and is on bail . 
 